posting_body: ["Embrace classic comfort and contemporary style at 3300 Tamarac Apartments, in Denver's Hampden neighborhood.", 'Our collection of refined studio, 1 & 2 bedroom apartments offer you a place to rest, relax, and have a little fun.', 'From our relaxed modern style and upscale social spaces to chic interiors, youll be ready to unwind in no time.', '-Reserved covered parking Photo Featured amenity', '-Fenced dog park with pet watering station', '-Pet friendly (breed restrictions apply)', '-3 relaxing pools with expansive sundecks', '-Easy access to public transportation', '-Landscaped courtyards and ponds with outdoor seating', '-Wood-style plank flooring in kitchen and living areas', '-Ceiling fans in living areas and bedrooms', '-Separate dining area', '-Worry-free 24-hour onsite maintenance', '-Energy efficient appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher select units Featured amenity', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Prices Change Daily', 'Flexible Lease Terms']
